title: (x) "Darkleigh" spikey bold italic caps - Pirate Keg {Tim (self)}

comments.content:
I wouldn't call that a sans serif, or did you mean to put a different image for this post? You used this picture in your other recent post too.

- Mike Yanega

Hi Mike,

What would you call it? I'm not a hardcore type guy. I'm waiting for my copy of the font book to turn up, hopefully that will help me.

The font turned out to be called Pirate Keg.
